meta-product demonstrates how one's own custom layer can be used to add
to existing images and thus form an automated build procedure for a 
custom product.

This layer requires a working Toradex BSP setup (with meta-toradex),
see
http://developer.toradex.com/software-resources/arm-family/linux/board-support-package/openembedded-(core)
repo branch LinuxImageV2.3
